text.tspan: - Turn on the filter & air compressor.
- Make sure correct Z height is chosen
- Make sure the lid is closed before cutting.
- Safe materials to cut: Acrylic, Wood, Paper, Cardboard
- In case of fire, notify superuser and extinguish with fire blanket.
- Dont bypass any safety features or leave the machine unattended.
- DONT cut any of the following materials (due to safety reasons):
Polystyrene, Polycarbonate, PVC, Vinyl, Fiberglass, HDPE, Leather
Ask a superuser if you can cut a material not on this list!
